name: Bounce Quest (GI203-Projects)
description:
Bounce Quest is a bouncing sports game that lets you challenge yourself and beat your own records.

Let start and..
Press the WASD button to walk towards the ball, collect points and test your abilities! ENJOYY!

Developer List : Wachsirin Sarayutpisai 1640700223 (Programmer) & Suttipong Sinklang 1640700462 (Artist)
